Package: QForm
Type: Package
Title: Methods for Bounding P-values and Scalable Screening with Quadratic Forms
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(person("Ryan R.", "Christ", email = "rchrist@wustl.edu", role = c("aut","cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2049-3389")), person("Louis J. M.", "Aslett", email = "louis@louisaslett.com", role = c("aut")))
Maintainer: Ryan R. Christ <rchrist@wustl.edu>
Description: QForm provides upper and lower bounds on p-values for test statistics of the form \dqen{\sum\limits_i f\left(\lambda_i\right) \left(Z_i + \delta_i)^2}{\Sigma f( \lambda_i ) (Z_i + \delta_i)^2}.
